# copyDescription

**Instance Property**

The callback used to create a descriptive string representation of each key in the dictionary. If `NULL`, the collection will create a simple description of each key. See [doc://com.apple.corefoundation/documentation/CoreFoundation/CFDictionaryCopyDescriptionCallBack] for a description of this callback.

## Declaration

```swift
var copyDescription: CFDictionaryCopyDescriptionCallBack!
```
